{"tid":922173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報青衣車禍指「今次死得人多囉」　《香港01》認衰承認用語不恰當","createTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T13:33:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"68bd45b2b599643a285cd03048a562e9830e0cfa","tid":922173,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"今晨（11月30日）青衣發生奪命車禍，釀成5死32人受傷，《香港01》報道這宗悲劇時，在Facebook用了「今次死得人多囉」，而遭到洗版圍攻。  <br />\n<br />\n不少網民到《香港01》Facebook留言，指「你果句呢caption黎？你識唔識咩叫尊重？句caption聽落好無禮貌！！！」、「咩叫死得人多囉，痴左線呀？」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後《香港01》把句子改成「RIP!!!」。  《香港01》之後在涉事貼文回覆網民致歉，指「小編凌晨版本的feed文，確實用語不恰當，有違媒體處理新聞事件的行文準則，也貶低了前線記者同事的專業報道。我們將引以為戒，避免同類情況，並希望大家繼續監督。🙏」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201811/47248442_1970163729950876_750421161313042432_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201811%2F47248442_1970163729950876_750421161313042432_n.jpg&h=215ed187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201811/46979507_2061276783933629_1227820992605192192_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201811%2F46979507_2061276783933629_1227820992605192192_n.jpg&h=0492908b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f4f3d86a0160ba042ebd42fdc7caad5e0204f6","tid":922173,"uid":38904,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"01一向低質架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33a0d567333fa0746c38b25b25e88afe2cd8036","tid":922173,"uid":53672,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"01質素係咁上下"},{"pid":"c0f32ce5950be2613270bae92fe14665681a6686","tid":922173,"uid":90863,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"上得連登抄料多搞到連登化埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc1